						<div id="project-capstone" class="project-detail hidden">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Explainable AI Tutor Platform</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
        <strong>I architected a production-ready AI platform that operationalizes NIST AI RMF governance into functional code.</strong> 
        Unlike "black box" EdTech tools, this system uses a Multi-Agent RAG architecture and a proprietary transparent Dual-Axis scoring engine to measure a student's subject mastery
    </p>

    <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Key Skills Demonstrated</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Trusted Advisor:</strong> Delivered executive-ready governance artifacts</li>
		<li><strong>Product Architecture:</strong> Designed the Multi-Agent orchestration (Python/Flask) and RAG logic.</li>
        <li><strong>AI Governance:</strong> Mapped NIST AI RMF & COPPA controls directly to product features.</li>
        <li><strong>XAI Design:</strong> Created the "Dual-Axis" scoring rubric (Correctness vs. Explanation Quality).</li>
		  <li><strong>XAI Design:</strong> Transparent, rubric-based scoring for explainability</li>
        <li><strong>Risk Management:</strong> Built "Safety Agent" guardrails for PII and self-harm detection.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Challenge</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Standard GenAI tutors hallucinate facts and cannot distinguish between memorization and understanding.</p></div>
        <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">My Solution</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">A "Glass Box" architecture that restricts answers to approved curriculum and logs every scoring decision for transparency.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="explainable-ai-tutor-platform/index.html" target="_blank" class="bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors shadow-sm">
            <i data-lucide="layout" class="w-4 h-4"></i> View Product Hub & Specs
        </a>

        <a href="https://ai-tutor-demo-a6cs.onrender.com/" target="_blank" class="bg-white text-slate-700 border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Launch Live RAG Backend
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-900"><strong>Outcome:</strong> A defensible, scalable AI reference architecture ready for enterprise deployment.</p>
    </div>
</div>

                        <div id="project-pegasus" class="project-detail hidden">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Pegasus Framework</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
                                <strong>I built and scaled a 6-phase analytical playbook that standardized AI bot optimization for enterprise clients.</strong> 
                                Transformed inconsistent analyst output into consistent, high-impact, product-relevant insights.
                            </p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Key Skills Demonstrated</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1 mb-6">
                                <li><strong>AI Strategy:</strong> End-to-end process for consulting, analysis, value delivery</li>
                                <li><strong>Root Cause Analysis:</strong> Beyond symptoms to KPI-impacting issues</li>
                                <li><strong>Stakeholder Management:</strong> Tactical + executive alignment</li>
                                <li><strong>Impact Forecasting:</strong> Pre/post-deployment KPI tracking + ROI</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                                <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Challenge</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Insights team delivered high-value AI bot optimization recommendations, but analysts lacked deep analytics/product thinking skills—leading to inconsistent report quality and limited scaling of services.</p></div>
                                <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">My Role</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Designed codified playbook (Pegasus Framework) + structured training program; upskilled team to deliver consistent, product-relevant insights improving client decision-making and AI service value.</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-3">
                                <a href="assets/fw_project_pegasus.pdf" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
