                        <div id="project-invision" class="project-detail hidden">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">InVision VR EdTech Plan</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
                                <strong>I co-authored a 32-page business plan for InVision Learning, a VR-based education platform delivering immersive learning for K-12 and corporate training.</strong> 
                                Defined product, market opportunity, GTM strategy, rollout phases, revenue streams, and financial projections.
                            </p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Key Skills Demonstrated</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1 mb-6">
                                <li><strong>Business Strategy:</strong> Analyzed sectors (K-12, corporate L&D), competitors, barriers, and demand drivers</li>
                                <li><strong>Go-to-Market:</strong> Built marketing plan, partnerships, billing processes, data protocols, and market differentiators</li>
                                <li><strong>Financial Modeling:</strong> Projected revenue streams (subscriptions, partnerships) and performance metrics for investor pitch</li>
                                <li><strong>Action Planning:</strong> Phased rollout (R&D, soft launch, enhancements) with staff/operational details</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                                <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Challenge</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">EdTech lacks immersive VR solutions for diverse sectors; need comprehensive plan covering market use cases, barriers (e.g., adoption costs), competitors, and scalable rollout to capture growing demand in K-12/corporate training.</p></div>
                                <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">My Role</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Co-led plan development: Defined product/ops, executed market analysis, crafted GTM/financials, and outlined phased action plan for investor-ready scalability.</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex gap-3 mb-6">
                                <a href="assets/bp_invision_learning.pdf" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
