                                <p class="text-sm text-purple-900"><strong>Outcome:</strong> Investor-ready blueprint with clear path to revenue; positioned InVision as VR leader in immersive education.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div id="project-monarch" class="project-detail hidden">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Monarque Solutions (Full-Stack)</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
                                <strong>I partnered with a consulting firm to design and build a full-stack AI solution to combat employee burnout from caregiving.</strong><BR>
                                <br>1. <strong>Quantify Risk:</strong> I built an <strong>AI-powered ROI Calculator</strong> to prove the significant financial risk of manager-employee disconnect.
                                <br>2. <strong>Build Solution:</strong> I developed the <strong>AI Voice Coach</strong>, a secure, full-stack application for managers to practice empathetic conversations.
                                <br>3. <strong>Govern Deployment:</strong> I created the complete governance suite (Impact Assessment, PRD, Data Flow) to ensure a defensible, ethical, and private-by-design deployment.
                            </p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Key Skills Demonstrated</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 space-y-1 mb-6">
                                <li><strong>Full-Stack AI Product Dev:</strong> From ROI modeling to a secure, deployed web app.</li>
                                <li><strong>AI Governance (NIST RMF):</strong> Authored a full AI Impact Assessment (see link below).</li>
                                <li><strong>Rapid Prototyping:</strong> Coded and deployed both interactive tools as a solo IC.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                                <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">Challenge</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Clients understood the <strong>idea</strong> of caregiver burnout risk but lacked tools to quantify the financial impact or scalably train managers to fix it.</p></div>
                                <div><h5 class="font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">My Role</h5><p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Lead Strategist, Designer, and Developer. I engineered the ROI formulas, built the AI calculator, then designed, built, and wrote the governance for the AI Voice Coach solution.</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
                                <a href="https://roicalcmonarquesolutions.netlify.app/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
